rComments: Great Prof! Gives very clear instructions. Her lectures are very organized and clear therefore it is easy to follow. Quickly response to emails and available for help.

Great prof, all of the other reviews are so old, she wasn't like that at all when I had her.  Her lectures are super clear and she always asks if students have questions during lecture.  She incorporates a lot of discussion, instead of talking at you, she talks with you during lecture.
some researchers should not be allowed to teach~
